trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Transmitido exporters WSDL personalizados e importers para ativar a personalização da exportação metadados e importar os processos para um ponto final de WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: A classe de WsdlEndpointConversionContext representa o contexto em que o WSDL personalizado para um ponto final é que qualquer exportado a utilizar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>ou importado utilizando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: As seguintes propriedades permitem-lhe obter o modelo de objeto de documento WSDL para o WSDL atual: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>para o contrato de ponto final.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName>para o ponto final atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>propriedade obtém o enlace para o ponto final atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>propriedade obtém a porta para o ponto final atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>

trans-unit.source: - - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: -Os seguintes métodos permitem-lhe adicionar ou remover elementos WSDL personalizados para os âmbitos adequados no WSDL importado ou exportado: - <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>método devolve o enlace de erro para o índice de falhas especificado.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>método devolve o índice de falhas para o enlace de falhas especificado.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>método devolve o enlace de mensagem para a mensagem especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>método devolve a mensagem para o enlace de mensagem especificado.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>método devolve o enlace de operação para a operação especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>método devolve a operação para o enlace de operação especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>
